ework</li>\n		<li>Dev: Added ywdpd_table_orientation filter to change the quantity table layout</li>\n		<li>Fix: Cart rules not scheluding correctly</li>\n		<li>Fix: Cart rule condition check for amount of orders did not work properly</li>\n		<li>Tweak: Improve script to update also prices for the variation product with quantity table</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.1.4 - Released on 03 March 2021</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: YITH plugin framework</li>\n		<li>Fix: Wrong html escaping</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.1.3 - Released on 03 March 2021</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Support for WooCommerce 5.1</li>\n		<li>New: Support for WordPress 5.7</li>\n		<li>Update: YITH plugin framework</li>\n		<li>Fix: Issue with Gift product rule not working correctly with variable products when variations were completely or partially configured</li>\n		<li>Fix: Style issue with select2 and YITH Proteo</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.1.2 - Released on 15 February 2021</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: YITH plugin framework</li>\n    <li>Update: Language files</li>\n    <li>Fix: Discounted price not showing up in cart if the price is displayed tax excluded on the cart page</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.1.1 - Released on 11 February 2021</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: YITH plugin framework</li>\n		<li>Update: Language files</li>\n		<li>Fix: Wrong popup position on specific screen resolutions</li>\n		<li>Fix: Discounted price not showing up in cart if the price is displayed tax excluded on the cart page</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.1.0 - Released on 02 February 2021</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Show special offer products in a modal window, after an add to cart event on the product page</li>\n		<li>New: Support for WooCommerce 5.0</li>\n		<li>Tweak: New popup style</li>\n		<li>Update: YITH plugin framework</li>\n		<li>Update: Language files</li>\n		<li>Dev: Added filter yith_ywdpd_can_init_plugin</li>\n		<li>Dev: Added filter ywdpd_gift_subtotal</li>\n		<li>Fix: Gift products not removed after a cart update</li>\n		<li>Fix: Check if a variation is out of stock in popup</li>\n    </ul><h4>2.0.3 - Released on 04 January 2021</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.9</li>\n		<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n		<li>Fix: Issue with Gift rules</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.0.2 - Released on 24 December 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n		<li>Dev: Added filter ywdpd_skip_cart_process_discounts</li>\n		<li>Fix: Price rules by product tag not applied in the cart</li>\n		<li>Fix: Price on single product page not updated properly with the quantity table</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.0.1 - Released on 21 December 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n		<li>Dev: Added filter yith_ywdpd_quantity_pattern</li>\n		<li>Fix: Cart rules for specific customers are applied also to guest users</li>\n		<li>Fix: Gift rules on minimum subtotal are always applied in the cart</li>\n		<li>Fix: Integration with YITH WOOCOMMERCE BRANDS ADD-ON Premium</li>\n    </ul><h4> 2.0.0 - Released on 09 December 2020</h4>\n    	<ul><li>New: Plugin UI restyling</li>\n			<li>New: Possibility to create price rule for the whole store</li>\n			<li>New: Possibility to create price rule for product categories</li>\n			<li>New: Possibility to create gift rule for minimum subtotal</li>\n			<li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.8</li>\n			<li>New: Support for WordPress 5.6</li>\n			<li>Tweak: Optimization of the price rules creation process</li>\n			<li>Update: Language files</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n    	</ul><h4>Version 1.7.2 - Released on 4 Nov 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Support for WordPress 5.6</li>\n      <li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.7</li>\n      <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n      <li>Fix: Fixed some php warnings</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.7.1 - Released on 13 Oct 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.6</li>\n      <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.7.0 - Released on 17 Sep 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>Support for WooCommerce 4.5</li>\n      <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.9 - Released on 24 Aug 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n      <li>Fix: Fixed issues with YITH WooCommerce Membership</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.8 - Released on 11 Aug 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n     <li>Fix: Issue on related products</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.7 - Released on 10 Aug 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Support for WordPress 5.5</li>\n      <li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.4</li>\n      <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n      <li>Fix: issue with showing discounted price in cart if taxes are enabled</li>\n      <li>Fix: issue with hiding discounted price on related products if \"show in loop\" option is turned off on single product page</li>\n      <li>Fix: Integration with YITH Subscription 2.0.3</li>\n      <li>Dev: New filters \'yith_ywdpd_get_price_exclusion_rule\' and \'ywdpd_table_orientation\'</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.6 - Released on 8 Jun 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>Fix: Fixed issue with percentage amount</li>\n      <li>Fix: Fixed Exclusion rule issues</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.5 - Released on 21 May 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.2</li>\n      <li>New: Elementor Support</li>\n      <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n      <li>Fix: Fixed issue with minimum price for variable products</li>\n      <li>Fix: Issue on quantity table</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.4 - Released on 11 May 2020</h4>\n    <ul><li>New: Option to change product price when customer changes quantity</li>\n		<li>New: Option to select the default quantity in the table</li>\n		<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n		<li>Update: Language file</li>\n		<li>Dev: Added yith_ywdpd_valid_num_of_orders_status filter</li>\n    </ul><h4>Version 1.6.3 - Released on 4 May 2020</h4>\n			<ul><li>New: Support for WooCommerce 4.1</li>\n              <li>Tweak: Update price when the product quantity is changed</li>\n              <li>Tweak: Quantity table improved</li>\n              <